      <div class="msgContentFrame"><a href="HTTP://forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=27607279749&amp;sid=1&amp;pageNo=1" rel="external nofollow" title="forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=27607279749&amp;sid=1&amp;pageNo=1">Happens this Wednesday, November 17th</a>. <br /> <br />They're encouraging all players to move over to the new forums, of course. It's not like the forums are gone completely. But they're shutting down the old ones and moving over to the new system, including karma. It's about damn time. <br /> <br />I predict Tuesday night will be full of people trying to get the last post ever before they lock the forums, followed by a lot of QQing on the new forums about how the new system sucks. <br /> <br />Then a lot of downrating. <br /> <br />Edit because I suck at links. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 15th 2010 11:03pm by IDrownFish </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm"><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Ray Bradbury wrote:</div><div class="orig">I'm being ironic. Don't interrupt a man in the midst of being ironic, it's not polite.</div></div></span></div></div>
